<h2>1-Bedroom Apartment Available In The CWE, St. Louis! Perfect Location For Restaurants, Grocery Stores, &amp; Local Attractions Within Walking Distance!</h2>

<h3>Fairmont Apartments  |  7 Maryland Plaza, St. Louis, MO  |  Central West End



<br> 
<br>
<br>



</h3><h4><u>General Information</u></h4>
<ul>
<li><b>Apartment Type:</b>1-Bedroom Apartment</li>
<li><b>Square Footage:</b> 542 square feet</li>
<li><b>Utilities Included:</b> Water, sewer, gas, and trash 
</li><li><b>Lease Duration:</b> 6 months to 12 months with options to renew</li>
<li><b>Rent:</b> $830 per month for a 12-month lease</li>
<li><b>Deposit:</b> $400 for a 12-month lease</li>
<li><b>Application Fee:</b> $40 per each applicant or married couple (non refundable)</li>
<li><b>Laundry:</b> Washer and dryer located on every floor</li>
<li><b>Parking:</b> Gated, off-street parking for $80 per month (inquire about space availability)</li>
</ul>

<br>
<hr>
<br>


<h4><u>Apartment Features</u></h4>
<ul>
<li>Comfortable living area</li>
<li>Kitchen equipped with a standard sized refrigerator, full size 4-burner stove top oven &amp; cabinet space, </li>
<li>Laminate wood flooring throughout living space</li>
<li>Tenth Floor Apartment</li>
<li>Closet for clothes &amp; storage, linen closet in bathroom</li>
<li>Windows allowing natural light</li>
<li>Wall-unit air conditioning and baseboard heating systems for personal temperature control</li>
<li>All appliances are electric</li>
<li>Internet / cable ready</li>
</ul>


<br>
<hr>
<br>


<h4><u>Community &amp; Neighborhood Features</u></h4>
The Fairmont and Monticello Apartments offer both studio and one bedroom apartment homes in a vibrant atmosphere and a <b>GREAT LOCATION</b>! The Central West End is a community where tradition meets modern style, and we are located right in the heart of it all. Both of our buildings provide cozy apartment homes that are appointed with today's modern necessities while also maintaining a historic design full of character and charm!<br>
<br>
Our central location means that our residents enjoy easy access to highway 64/40, Forest Park, Whole Foods, Schnucks Grocery Market, Washington University, Saint Louis University, BJC Hospital, and more!  Our vibrant neighborhood offers retail shopping, delectable restaurants, and convenient coffee shops all within a few steps of our front door.  We are also within walking distance to major bus lines and The Metrolink. With close proximity to just about everything, our location simply cannot be beat!<br>
<ul>
<li>Fitness room </li>
<li>Cats and dogs are welcome (please contact us for information regarding stipulations, pet deposit, and pet rent)</li>
<li>Elevator</li>
<li>Friendly on-site management</li>
<li>24-hour emergency maintenance</li>
<li>Easy access to Wash U, SLU, BJC Hospital, and Forest Park </li>
<li>Located near several restaurants, shops, bars, and grocery stores</li>
<li>Public transportation is within walking distance</li>
</ul>


<br>
<hr>
<br>



